AbaThembu King Buyelekhaya Dalindyebo visited former president Jacob Zuma at his Nkandla home this weekend. Mzwanele Manyi, the Jacob Zuma Foundation's spokesperson joined eNCA's Heidi Giokos to discuss the meeting. Courtesy of #DStv403 NKANDLA - AbaThembu King Buyelekhaya Dalindyebo paid a courtesy visit to former president Jacob Zuma at Nkandla. The purpose of the king's visit was to check in on the former President following his recent release from prison on medical parole. WATCH: King Dalindyebo's courtesy visit to Zuma King Dalindyebo's spokesperson, Prince Mthunzi Ngonyama, says the visit was to show moral support for Zuma and had nothing to do with politics. Watch the video above for more details. Abathembu King Buyelekhaya Dalindyebo is visiting former president Jacob Zuma on Saturday. eNCA senior reporter Dasen Thathiah is following these developments. Courtesy of #DStv403